export default function transformProps(chartProps) {
  const { width, height, formData, queriesData } = chartProps;
  const { encoding, rotation, sliceId } = formData;
  return {
    data: queriesData[0].data,
    encoding,
    height,
    rotation,
    width,
    sliceId };

}
